91ng-Chi-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-ugO5moh7gzYYDOe2gVJzDg">Tống Chi Vấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-N%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Kh%E1%BB%91c-Th%E1%BA%A9m-sinh/poem-ZEAfuKVaXqOBRzIQDaSbPA">Khốc Thẩm sinh - 哭沈生</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-N%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PSgXCHLe22-Whw_BN8uK9A">Trương Ngọc Nương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tra-Th%E1%BA%ADn-H%C3%A0nh/T%E1%BA%A3o-xu%E1%BA%A5t-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nghi-M%C3%B4n-Ngu%E1%BB%B5-V%C5%A9-B%C3%ACnh-%C4%90%C3%A0m-Ch%E1%BA%A5n-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%A9m-Kh%C3%A1ch-T%E1%BB%AD-truy-t%E1%BB%91ng-%C6%B0-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%C3%BD-chi-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-m%C3%A3/poem---QqCdwPLcvho1KFJk4ePg">Tảo xuất Chương Nghi Môn Nguỵ Vũ Bình Đàm Chấn Phương Thẩm Khách Tử truy tống ư thập lý chi ngoại mã thượng lưu biệt kỳ 2 - 早出彰儀門魏禹平談震方沈客子追送於十里之外馬上㽞別其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tra-Th%E1%BA%ADn-H%C3%A0nh/author-9xzWBLqDsfopprRgu6Tsgg">Tra Thận Hành</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-thi%C3%AAn-ti%E1%BA%BFt-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-4JKOKQe2OgCA_G7PyiCnZg">Thu thiên tiết hữu cảm kỳ 2 - 千秋節有感其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%C3%B4-Tr%C3%BAc-chi-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-09/poem-6vVimX4xLfffYBjZddSYuQ">Thương Ngô Trúc chi ca kỳ 09 - 蒼梧竹枝歌其九</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
